# Recipe AI Engine - FastAPI Requests (VS Code REST Client)
# Requires the "REST Client" extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Generate Recipe - Basic Example
POST {{baseUrl}}/recipes/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

{
  "ingredients": ["chicken breast", "rice", "vegetables"],
  "cuisine_type": "Asian",
  "difficulty_level": "medium",
  "serving_size": 2
}

### Generate Recipe - Vegan Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/recipes/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

{
  "ingredients": ["tofu", "broccoli", "soy sauce", "garlic"],
  "cuisine_type": "Asian",
  "dietary_restrictions": ["vegan"],
  "difficulty_level": "easy",
  "serving_size": 3
}

### Generate Recipe - Italian Style
POST {{baseUrl}}/recipes/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

{
  "ingredients": ["pasta", "tomato", "basil", "olive oil", "garlic"],
  "cuisine_type": "Italian",
  "difficulty_level": "medium",
  "serving_size": 4
}
